# ==============================================================================
# Brewfile.server - Minimal Server Environment
# ==============================================================================
# Essential tools for headless Linux servers, VPS, and CI/CD runners.
# This is a minimal supplement to Brewfile.core for production environments.
#
# This file contains INCREMENTAL packages beyond Brewfile.core.
# All core utilities (git, neovim, btop, etc.) are inherited from core.
#
# Design Principle: Zero Trust, Minimal Attack Surface
# Focus on:
#   1. System monitoring and diagnostics
#   2. Log analysis and troubleshooting
#   3. Backup and disaster recovery
#   4. Security hardening (optional)
#
# Profile: server (headless Linux)
# Dependencies: Brewfile.core
# ==============================================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Enhanced Monitoring
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
brew "bottom"
brew "glances"
brew "bmon"

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Log Management & Analysis
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
brew "lnav"

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Backup & Disaster Recovery
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
brew "restic"

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Security Hardening (Optional - Uncomment for Public Servers)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
